{"word":"G1563 - ἐκεῖ - ekeî - ek-i' - There","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκεῖ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ekeî</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ek-i'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">There</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அங்கே, அவ்விடம் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"there"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Of uncertain affinity; <i>there</i>; by extension <i>thither:</i> - there, thither (-ward), (to) yonder (place).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}